Cron Job
---------------
Cretae a cron job using the image bitnami/nginx 
Latest with the following requirements
The cron job name is "job-runner"
The cron job runs at 04:05 on the 2nd day of each month
The successful job history limit is 14
The service account and service account name is "trigger-sa"
The cron job runs in the project called "scheduler"

---------------------------------
oc whoami --show-console
Workloads
   CronJob
      Project:scheduler
        Create CronJob
apiVersion: batch/v1
kind:CronJob
metadata:
   name: job-runner
   namespace: scheduler
spec:
   scheduler: '5 4 2 * *'
   jobTemplate:
     spec:
       template:
          spec:
            serviceAccountName: trigger-sa
            containers:
               - name: job-runner
                 image: bitnami/nginx
            restartPolicy: OnFailure
    successfulJobHistroryLimit: 14
